- I...

28:17.263 --> 28:19.063
I say we go, it'll be fun.
Come on, Bree.

28:19.065 --> 28:20.264
In high school,
all the kids used to go,

28:20.266 --> 28:21.699
it was like a dare.
Kinda like,

28:21.701 --> 28:23.333
make out in the prison,
kind of thing.

28:23.335 --> 28:25.169
Ah.

28:25.171 --> 28:27.271
We could make some more
recordings added to the box.

28:27.273 --> 28:28.706
Yes.

28:28.708 --> 28:31.241
