40:35.801 --> 40:37.600
"The lost return...

40:37.602 --> 40:39.469
Awakening of the dead

40:39.471 --> 40:41.104
and the end begins.

40:41.106 --> 40:42.205
Drawing the devil

40:42.207 --> 40:43.706
from out of the cycle."

40:43.708 --> 40:44.774
Hello?

40:49.147 --> 40:50.847
- Jesus. I don't like this, Eric.
- Calm down.

40:50.849 --> 40:53.049
This isn't like anything
we've ever experienced.

40:53.051 --> 40:55.485
- Please can we just go? -It's
just our friends trying to play...

40:55.487 --> 40:57.754
I don't fucking care, this place
gives me the creeps, all right?

40:57.756 --> 40:59.189
Take some photos to prove
we were here, and let's go.

40:59.191 --> 41:01.524
Okay. Okay.

41:02.894 --> 41:05.562
I love you.

41:05.564 --> 41:07.831
I love you too.

41:16.875 --> 41:18.107
You better.

41:56.548 --> 41:57.547
Eric!

41:57.549 --> 41:58.748
Oh, my god.

41:58.750 --> 41:59.916
What the fuck?
Eric.

41:59.918 --> 42:02.819
Hey, hey, hey...
I need your help!

42:02.821 --> 42:05.588
Holy shit.
Take him to a hospital.

42:05.590 --> 42:06.589
I can't, he's gonna bleed out.

42:06.591 --> 42:08.925
Get off of him!

42:08.927 --> 42:12.095
You're killing him. Please,
you're killing him.

42:12.097 --> 42:13.796
You're killing him!
Eric!

42:13.798 --> 42:15.231
Hold up, hold up.

42:15.233 --> 42:16.900
Hang on, hang on.

42:18.570 --> 42:19.569
I got you, man.

42:19.571 --> 42:21.137
Relax.

42:21.139 --> 42:22.839
Calm down.

42:42.827 --> 42:43.927
He just stopped bleeding.

42:43.929 --> 42:45.261
I don't understand, dude.

42:45.263 --> 42:46.663
We just gotta get out of here.

42:46.665 --> 42:52.035
Sarah should be waiting for us.

42:52.037 --> 42:54.637
I still think it's safer
in here than out there.

42:54.639 --> 42:55.738
What the fuck do you mean?

42:56.908 --> 42:58.207
Did you not see
what just happened?

42:58.209 --> 43:00.710
Matt, I lived it.

43:00.712 --> 43:02.078
The only difference
between you and me,

43:02.080 --> 43:03.947
is that I don't want
to run from it.

43:03.949 --> 43:06.749
The difference is you're
fucking insane. Okay?

43:06.751 --> 43:08.151
The side effect is
you don't want to run.

43:08.153 --> 43:11.287
Stop fighting.

43:11.289 --> 43:13.923
Am I all alone here? Does anyone
else see how fucking insane this is?

43:13.925 --> 43:15.258
I'm ready to go home.

43:15.260 --> 43:16.893
There's something
down there, guys.

43:16.895 --> 43:18.328
It wants to be heard.

43:18.330 --> 43:20.830
It wants us to hear it.
Don't you get that?

43:20.832 --> 43:23.733
You wanna stick around with a couple
of flashlights, find out what it is?

43:23.735 --> 43:25.168
- Eric, please.
- Okay, yeah.

43:25.170 --> 43:26.903
- We're going.
- I'm not going.

43:26.905 --> 43:27.937
Baby, whatever's down there,

43:27.939 --> 43:30.807
it's not going anywhere.

43:32.310 --> 43:34.711
- Hey.
- Fine, fine.

43:37.148 --> 43:39.882
We're coming back.
Okay?

44:15.086 --> 44:16.853
Thank you so much.

44:16.855 --> 44:19.656
I need to get to
a hospital immediately.

44:19.658 --> 44:21.378
I did not think
that anybody was gonna stop.

44:25.664 --> 44:27.997
You was saying?

44:27.999 --> 44:31.234
Yeah, um...

44:31.236 --> 44:33.269
I was just saying thank you.

44:33.271 --> 44:36.272
Thank you so much.

44:36.274 --> 44:38.908
Nice night for a walk.

44:38.910 --> 44:42.245
Yeah.

45:21.986 --> 45:23.786
What the f...

45:23.788 --> 45:25.021
Oh, no. No, no, no...

45:25.023 --> 45:26.355
How the hell
did we get back here?

45:26.357 --> 45:28.291
Like, I don't know, all right?

45:28.293 --> 45:30.026
- Will you just please... -everybody
please, just chill out, okay?

45:30.028 --> 45:31.894
What's going on?

45:31.896 --> 45:33.229
Maybe there's
something in that book.

45:33.231 --> 45:34.711
What are you talking about?
What book?

45:36.468 --> 45:38.268
What? Do you guys know
something that I don't?

45:39.137 --> 45:41.404
What book?

45:41.406 --> 45:43.439
Here, take it.

45:49.247 --> 45:51.013
"To write to the offered...

45:51.015 --> 45:52.982
On seducing the soul
of the newborn

45:52.984 --> 45:56.085
a vessel will deliver
the chosen."

45:56.087 --> 45:58.521
Okay, we, uh... we have to
get the hell out of here.

45:58.523 --> 46:00.022
How?

46:00.024 --> 46:01.390
There... there has
to be another path.

46:01.392 --> 46:03.092
We have to try again.

46:04.829 --> 46:07.530
Jesus, what kind
of evil is in this place?

46:10.835 --> 46:12.168
Can somebody tell me
what is happening?

46:12.170 --> 46:13.970
Is this real?
Is this real...

46:13.972 --> 46:15.471
Calm down. We will
find a way out of here.

46:15.473 --> 46:17.140
Eric, what are you doing?

46:17.142 --> 46:18.775
Eric!

46:18.777 --> 46:20.877
This is where
we're supposed to be.

46:20.879 --> 46:23.513
Right here. This is the strongest
signal I've ever gotten.

46:23.515 --> 46:26.215
Now, we were brought
here for a reason.

46:26.217 --> 46:28.017
Now, I don't know
about you guys,

46:28.019 --> 46:30.019
but I'm gonna go find out
what that reason is.

46:30.021 --> 46:34.056
If you go down there,
I'm not following you.

46:34.058 --> 46:35.391
Eric!

46:36.494 --> 46:39.462
Skye, let him go.

46:53.077 --> 46:55.578
My brother said

46:55.580 --> 46:57.914
that a pretty
young woman's expecting

46:57.916 --> 47:00.349
just to settle in these parts.

47:01.853 --> 47:04.954
Um, my husband and our friends

47:04.956 --> 47:07.990
went over to look
for that prison.

47:07.992 --> 47:09.992
That burned down?

47:09.994 --> 47:12.361
Yeah.

47:12.363 --> 47:13.596
Anyway, I was supposed
to go get them,

47:13.598 --> 47:16.432
so, can we pick them
up on the way?

47:16.434 --> 47:18.301
There's one good thing
that came out of that fire

47:18.303 --> 47:20.169
at least.

47:20.171 --> 47:23.539
It killed that devil
preacher Kane.

47:23.541 --> 47:26.309
Killed him good.

47:27.445 --> 47:29.846
We heard about him.

47:31.182 --> 47:34.050
Most have.

47:34.052 --> 47:37.320
Move in these parts had...
Had someone they love

47:37.322 --> 47:38.888
pulled off into the next world

47:38.890 --> 47:42.358
by his bush axe.

47:42.360 --> 47:45.995
That man had no good in him.

47:45.997 --> 47:48.331
Pure evil, he was.

47:49.567 --> 47:51.567
How did they catch him?

47:51.569 --> 47:54.103
It weren't no "they."

47:54.105 --> 47:58.040
- Captain got him.
- The captain?

47:58.042 --> 47:59.442
Well, he ain't been
there for a while,

47:59.444 --> 48:01.210
but we still call him.

48:01.212 --> 48:05.181
They let me ride along
for old time's sake.

48:05.183 --> 48:07.450
Feels like home

48:07.452 --> 48:10.319
in the squad car.

48:10.321 --> 48:13.155
- -He brought a
lot of these parts.

48:14.626 --> 48:16.659
He's the one who kept
this place from falling

48:16.661 --> 48:18.594
to the sodomites.

48:25.036 --> 48:27.637
What is that?

48:27.639 --> 48:30.406
People up here
believe different.

48:30.408 --> 48:35.144
Tradition's all just
passed down generations.

48:41.386 --> 48:42.451
These aren't the same roads

48:42.453 --> 48:44.086
that we took to get up here.

48:44.088 --> 48:48.024
More than one road in the hills.

49:06.945 --> 49:08.577
What you calling at?

49:08.579 --> 49:10.079
Ah!

49:12.083 --> 49:14.350
Is your body speaking at you?

49:14.352 --> 49:17.286
Yeah, I need you to pull over.

49:17.288 --> 49:19.989
We're gonna be out
in a few minutes.

49:19.991 --> 49:21.624
No, I'm gonna be sick.

49:21.626 --> 49:23.326
I need you to pull over now.

49:25.964 --> 49:29.565
Please?

49:37.976 --> 49:39.542
Hey, come back!

49:41.446 --> 49:43.045
It ain't safe!

49:49.053 --> 49:50.486
Okay, we have to find
another way out of here.

49:50.488 --> 49:52.221
How?
It's pitch black out there.

49:52.223 --> 49:54.123
- You have a better idea?
- Yeah, we call for help.

49:54.125 --> 49:55.725
- No one can get any reception.
- We can, we just have to...

49:55.727 --> 49:58.094
We just have to keep trying.

49:58.096 --> 50:00.029
You know, cause Sarah's...
Sarah's out there,

50:00.031 --> 50:01.564
you know, and she's...
She's waiting for us.

50:01.566 --> 50:03.366
- Don't touch me!
- Hey, calm down, calm down.

50:03.368 --> 50:05.201
Skye!

50:09.507 --> 50:11.774
Chewing on those like tic tacs.
What is that?

50:14.045 --> 50:16.612
Thorazine?

50:16.614 --> 50:19.749
How many of these
are you taking?

50:19.751 --> 50:21.317
How long have you been on this?

50:21.319 --> 50:23.486
Since I was eight
years old. All right?

50:23.488 --> 50:25.928
I've been a fucking schizophrenic
since I was eight years old.

51:16.607 --> 51:18.441
Sarah?

51:21.079 --> 51:23.846
Hey, we're lost.
Can you help us?

51:30.088 --> 51:31.187
Oh, shit.

51:34.125 --> 51:35.658
- What's up, what's up?
- There's people out there.

51:35.660 --> 51:37.126
What?

51:37.128 --> 51:38.427
Who are they?

51:38.429 --> 51:39.428
We don't want to find out.

51:39.430 --> 51:40.696
What are we gonna do?

51:40.698 --> 51:42.198
Okay, think. Think,
think, think.

51:42.200 --> 51:43.632
Okay, look, we hide in there

51:43.634 --> 51:45.267
and we wait them out.

51:45.269 --> 51:46.669
- Are you fucking insane?
- Am I fucking insane?

51:46.671 --> 51:48.304
What, do you wanna
hang around and say hi?

51:48.306 --> 51:50.139
Is there any other way?

51:50.141 --> 51:51.774
May... maybe
we could sidestep them.

51:51.776 --> 51:53.309
What if we can't
leave this place?

51:53.311 --> 51:54.577
What if every path
leads us back here?

51:54.579 --> 51:56.245
We are gonna leave this place.

51:56.247 --> 51:58.848
- They're coming. -Let them
bring it the fuck on.

51:58.850 --> 52:00.616
All right, you take them
and hide the girls,

52:00.618 --> 52:03.586
I'm gonna try to avert them,
and send for help.

52:03.588 --> 52:05.354
Let's go, let's go,
let's go, come on.

52:14.298 --> 52:16.432
Hey, come on, come on, come on.

52:16.434 --> 52:19.502
We gotta find Eric. He doesn't
know there are people out there.

52:19.504 --> 52:22.471
If he wants to go on his little trip, fine,
but this bus is not taking any detours.

52:22.473 --> 52:25.508
- You're just gonna leave him?
- Hey!

52:25.510 --> 52:26.575
Look, we're gonna get out
of this hellhole

52:26.577 --> 52:27.743
one way, or another,

52:27.745 --> 52:29.378
but I am not searching for him.

52:29.380 --> 52:30.613
Come on.

52:45.463 --> 52:49.431
Where are we?

52:49.433 --> 52:52.401
I don't think
this is the way out, Dave.

52:52.403 --> 52:54.537
I'm working on it.

53:23.367 --> 53:24.700
Eric?

53:54.932 --> 53:56.632
Matt?

54:06.277 --> 54:08.010
Guys?

54:18.356 --> 54:19.888
Guys?

54:29.634 --> 54:31.767
Oh, shit.

54:34.772 --> 54:36.272
What the hell are you doing?

54:36.274 --> 54:37.706
Just give me a minute, Bree.

54:37.708 --> 54:40.776
Oh, hell no.
Come on.

54:43.881 --> 54:46.749
"Murder, rape...

54:46.751 --> 54:49.885
Stabbed to death.

54:49.887 --> 54:51.487
Buried alive."

54:51.489 --> 54:53.022
Jesus Christ.

54:53.024 --> 54:55.691
It's almost like someone
wanted us to find this.

54:55.693 --> 54:57.526
Bree?

55:01.666 --> 55:03.966
Where the fuck is she?

55:03.968 --> 55:05.901
Shit.

55:14.645 --> 55:16.445
Eric?

55:19.917 --> 55:21.884
Eric?

55:23.521 --> 55:24.687
Eric!

55:25.956 --> 55:27.656
- Eric, we gotta go now.
- Hey.

55:29.360 --> 55:30.726
You came back.

55:30.728 --> 55:33.329
There are people up there.

55:33.331 --> 55:34.630
- What people?
- I don't know.

55:34.632 --> 55:36.098
They were speaking
in some weird language.

55:36.100 --> 55:38.334
And then I was calling
for them for help,

55:38.336 --> 55:40.369
but then they just started
coming after us and...

55:40.371 --> 55:42.004
Whoa, whoa, whoa...
Slow down.

55:42.006 --> 55:45.674
We had to come down here,
they were coming.

55:45.676 --> 55:48.344
Eric?

55:48.346 --> 55:49.945
This is it.

55:52.750 --> 55:54.883
Are you fucking shitting me?

55:54.885 --> 55:57.753
- We have to get out of...
- It's fine.

55:57.755 --> 56:00.389
This is what I came for.

56:19.844 --> 56:21.910
Get it together.

56:31.522 --> 56:33.722
That's not real.

56:52.710 --> 56:54.510
Matt?

57:02.553 --> 57:04.953
What spirits
are trapped in here?

57:11.629 --> 57:13.695
Come on, I know you can hear me.

57:16.500 --> 57:18.634
Just speak to me, okay?

57:21.038 --> 57:24.039
Come on, god damn it,
talk to us!

57:24.041 --> 57:25.774
Those people are coming.

57:25.776 --> 57:27.543
This place is
some sort of sanctuary,

57:27.545 --> 57:29.945
we don't belong here.

57:34.919 --> 57:36.652
What the fuck?

57:41.025 --> 57:43.091
They're people.

57:43.093 --> 57:45.828
They're fucking people.

57:45.830 --> 57:47.763
We have to get the fuck
out of here, now.

57:47.765 --> 57:50.132
Do you hear me?

57:50.134 --> 57:52.968
This is a trap, this is
exactly what they wanted.

57:55.506 --> 57:56.905
I'm outta here.

57:59.944 --> 58:02.044
Skye!

58:03.247 --> 58:05.047
Skye, come on.

58:26.036 --> 58:27.035
Get out.

58:27.037 --> 58:29.137
What the fuck?

58:29.139 --> 58:30.973
All right.

59:09.246 --> 59:10.312
Matt!

59:17.187 --> 59:19.988
Oh, come on, Dave.

59:19.990 --> 59:21.056
Jesus Christ.

59:56.860 --> 59:58.627
Shit.

01:00:17.014 --> 01:00:19.281
Ma'am, did you drop something?

01:00:23.654 --> 01:00:25.687
What the hell is this?

01:00:40.004 --> 01:00:41.403
You know the plan.

01:00:41.405 --> 01:00:43.105
They're gone until spring.

01:00:48.045 --> 01:00:51.213
Captain's gonna have your ass
if you're wrong, boy.

01:00:51.215 --> 01:00:53.281
Say so?

01:00:53.283 --> 01:00:56.852
See for yourself.

01:00:56.854 --> 01:00:58.253
She's got the mark.

01:01:01.792 --> 01:01:03.659
Our prayers have been answered.

01:01:03.661 --> 01:01:04.860
What she do?

01:01:04.862 --> 01:01:06.795
She's just a kid.

01:01:06.797 --> 01:01:08.430
Lord, have mercy.

01:01:08.432 --> 01:01:10.966
It's what she's going to do.

01:01:10.968 --> 01:01:13.335
Tell sister
to prepare the vessel.

01:01:13.337 --> 01:01:16.204
Full moon could
prove fertile tonight.

01:01:19.777 --> 01:01:21.810
Sister.

01:01:31.388 --> 01:01:34.856
Sweet child need love.

01:01:34.858 --> 01:01:36.124
You get now.

01:01:36.126 --> 01:01:37.359
This is my work.

01:01:41.765 --> 01:01:44.032
Captain gonna
put on a show tonight.

01:01:50.974 --> 01:01:52.307
It's all right, girl.

01:01:54.344 --> 01:01:56.712
Let me help you now.

01:01:58.816 --> 01:02:01.183
One of you might get lucky too.

01:02:02.453 --> 01:02:05.353
We're gonna make you
a strong mama.

01:02:05.355 --> 01:02:07.022
Till the moon delivers.

01:02:07.024 --> 01:02:08.990
The seed's sewn.

01:02:08.992 --> 01:02:12.027
The circle continue to turn.

01:02:16.133 --> 01:02:18.100
I've got her.

01:02:18.102 --> 01:02:19.468
Save yourself.

01:02:19.470 --> 01:02:21.136
Ugh!

01:02:21.138 --> 01:02:23.138
Come here!

01:02:32.182 --> 01:02:33.815
Kane!

01:03:34.878 --> 01:03:36.878
Your choice will be right.

01:03:59.369 --> 01:04:01.436
Sarah!

01:04:01.438 --> 01:04:04.172
Holy fuck.

01:04:04.174 --> 01:04:05.574
You okay?

01:04:05.576 --> 01:04:07.108
Yeah.

01:04:07.110 --> 01:04:08.977
I been calling your name
down the hallway,

01:04:08.979 --> 01:04:10.846
it's like you're
in a trance or something.

01:04:10.848 --> 01:04:12.614
No, I was watching...

01:04:12.616 --> 01:04:14.015
There's some seriously weird

01:04:14.017 --> 01:04:16.418
fucking shit going on right now.

01:04:16.420 --> 01:04:18.153
Where's Matt?

01:04:20.123 --> 01:04:21.957
I don't know.

01:04:21.959 --> 01:04:23.925
You don't know?

01:04:23.927 --> 01:04:26.127
No...

01:04:26.129 --> 01:04:28.063
What's this?

01:04:28.065 --> 01:04:29.965
I don't...

01:04:31.335 --> 01:04:33.134
"mutilated skin.

01:04:33.136 --> 01:04:34.236
Skinned alive..."

01:04:34.238 --> 01:04:36.137
Where did you get this?

01:04:36.139 --> 01:04:39.007
Dave had it.

01:04:39.009 --> 01:04:41.977
Eric, he's dead.

01:04:41.979 --> 01:04:43.378
He's what?

01:04:45.282 --> 01:04:48.183
"Dusty Cableton,
and Ana Harris found on"...

01:04:48.185 --> 01:04:50.252
Ana Harris?

01:04:50.254 --> 01:04:53.088
That's the name
of the grave in the woods.

01:04:53.090 --> 01:04:56.925
December 5, 1979. She died
on the day we were born.

01:04:56.927 --> 01:04:59.361
What the fuck is going on?

01:04:59.363 --> 01:05:00.462
Eric, I'm scared.

01:05:00.464 --> 01:05:03.064
Shh.

01:05:03.066 --> 01:05:05.000
Eric, I have family.
I have a baby.

01:05:05.002 --> 01:05:07.035
I need to get
the fuck out of here.

01:05:07.037 --> 01:05:09.070
- I don't know what's going on here.
- Yeah, okay.

01:05:09.072 --> 01:05:10.538
We will get out
of here. Okay?

01:05:12.109 --> 01:05:16.578
Oh, shit!

01:05:55.319 --> 01:05:56.484
Hey!

01:06:25.148 --> 01:06:27.082
It was you.

01:06:27.084 --> 01:06:29.551
Ana had the mark.

01:06:29.553 --> 01:06:32.187
I failed her in the barn.

01:06:32.189 --> 01:06:34.155
Ain't happening again.

01:06:45.435 --> 01:06:48.470
They're gonna kill us all!

01:06:48.472 --> 01:06:51.039
- What the fuck?
- Hey, man, what you doing?

01:06:53.010 --> 01:06:54.476
Fuck you, pig.

01:07:00.417 --> 01:07:03.485
You just could not keep
your mouth shut, could you?

01:07:03.487 --> 01:07:05.353
I was just gonna give you life
and leave it at that.

01:07:05.355 --> 01:07:07.489
But now, now I gotta
take that from you.

01:07:07.491 --> 01:07:09.657
Those kids never judged me.

01:07:09.659 --> 01:07:12.027
Why'd you?

01:07:12.029 --> 01:07:14.262
I done evil.
And I done it for you.

01:07:14.264 --> 01:07:16.431
But I never killed those kids.

01:07:16.433 --> 01:07:19.134
Preacher!

01:07:19.136 --> 01:07:21.369
You should've just
done your job, boy.

01:07:32.549 --> 01:07:36.051
It don't matter
what nobody said.

01:07:36.053 --> 01:07:38.653
We...

01:07:38.655 --> 01:07:40.088
Make the law around here.

01:07:52.636 --> 01:07:57.639
You'll burn in hell, you hear me, god damn?
To hell I say!

01:08:17.194 --> 01:08:19.461
Let us in!

01:08:47.858 --> 01:08:50.692
Are you ready to bleed?

01:08:50.694 --> 01:08:53.560
No.

01:09:19.589 --> 01:09:22.724
No, stop.
Let me go. Let me go!

01:09:22.725 --> 01:09:24.425
No, please don't hurt my baby!

01:09:24.426 --> 01:09:26.426
Shh, shh, shh.
Sweet angel.

01:09:26.429 --> 01:09:28.196
We're not going
to hurt your baby.

01:09:28.198 --> 01:09:29.731
No, no, please no!

01:09:32.269 --> 01:09:34.836
Calm yourself.

01:09:37.741 --> 01:09:38.907
Run!

01:09:44.180 --> 01:09:45.846
Kane!

01:09:53.423 --> 01:09:54.622
Matt!

01:09:57.894 --> 01:10:00.562
Welcome to hell, captain.

01:10:00.564 --> 01:10:02.363
No!

01:10:29.559 --> 01:10:32.927
Hey! Hey! Hey!

01:10:44.507 --> 01:10:48.309
Lord, child.
What happened to you?

01:10:48.311 --> 01:10:49.777
Mercy, girl.

01:10:49.779 --> 01:10:51.546
Come with me.

01:11:00.023 --> 01:11:02.257
It's all right, girl.

01:11:02.259 --> 01:11:03.424
Push it.

01:11:05.028 --> 01:11:07.862
We're gonna get this child
out of you.

01:11:07.864 --> 01:11:11.032
Now, give it everything you got.

01:11:12.535 --> 01:11:13.801
Push!

01:11:13.803 --> 01:11:15.036
Now!

01:11:17.507 --> 01:11:19.674
Don't you go white eye on me.

01:11:24.481 --> 01:11:27.348
Here she comes.

01:11:33.356 --> 01:11:35.456
She isn't crying.

01:11:35.458 --> 01:11:37.592
'Cause she ain't breathing.

01:11:37.594 --> 01:11:40.295
No. No.

01:11:40.297 --> 01:11:43.798
No! No! No! No!

01:11:43.800 --> 01:11:44.866
Give me my baby!

01:11:44.868 --> 01:11:47.902
Give me my baby!
Give me my baby!

01:11:47.904 --> 01:11:51.806
Do you want your child to live?

01:11:54.811 --> 01:11:58.813
Hey, look at me.
We're the lucky ones.

01:11:58.815 --> 01:12:01.482
I just want her
to live a long happy life.

01:12:01.484 --> 01:12:03.017
Yeah, well she will.

01:12:03.019 --> 01:12:04.619
I promise.

01:12:04.621 --> 01:12:06.688
Everything's gonna be fine.

01:12:06.690 --> 01:12:08.089
I know.

01:12:10.527 --> 01:12:14.962
Yes. Yes.
